WEBVTT

00:00:13.492 --> 00:00:19.498 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Pray to Jehovah, 
the Hearer of prayer.

00:00:19.498 --> 00:00:25.588 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is our priv’lege,
for his name we bear.

00:00:25.588 --> 00:00:31.844 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Open your heart
as you would to a friend,

00:00:31.844 --> 00:00:37.766 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Trust that on Him
you can always depend.

00:00:37.766 --> 00:00:43.022 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Pray to Jehovah each day.

00:00:56.535 --> 00:01:02.499 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Pray to Jehovah,
give thanks that we live,

00:01:02.499 --> 00:01:08.839 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Asking forgiveness
as we do forgive.

00:01:08.839 --> 00:01:14.845 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
May we confess
to our God whom we trust.

00:01:14.845 --> 00:01:20.851 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He is our Maker
and knows we are dust.

00:01:20.851 --> 00:01:26.357 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Pray to Jehovah each day.

00:01:27.274 --> 00:01:33.489 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Pray to Jehovah
when troubles appear.

00:01:33.489 --> 00:01:39.536 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He is our Father
and ever so near.

00:01:39.536 --> 00:01:45.626 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Seek his protection,
and look for his aid;

00:01:45.626 --> 00:01:51.632 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He is our confidence;
don’t be afraid.

00:01:51.632 --> 00:01:56.845 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Pray to Jehovah each day.

